data.description: You must see this Large Family Home (3,235 sq. ft. of living space) which opens to an inviting foyer with a height of a 20 ft. ceiling, boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths (all with bidets installed), 3 large living areas, Large Dining Room, granite counters, a large office-5th bedroom, 2 kitchen pantries, extra storage space for freezers-refrigerators, and 3 separate hvac systems.  This home is perfect for spacious family living, as well as entertaining guests.  The converted garage is recorded as 756 sq. ft. alone and features a wall of cabinets and drawers to keep things organized in your Game Room.  Laundry Room includes a Utility Sink!  The Outdoor Living Space features a built-in gas cook-top and a storage building.  So many amazing custom features, make this your home today!  Buyer's agent to verify all information.
